        <Parent_String>carotenoid [300391334], plant pigment [300013123], natural organic pigment [300013121], pigment by composition or origin [300013110], pigments [300013109], colorant (material) [300013026], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
